text: This example demonstrates a configuration of a simplified use of a Premium-SMS payment procedure, performed with the Web Service agents. The Web Service configuration consists of three main steps: Defining a WS profile Configuring a Web Service Provider workflow Configuring a Web Service Requester workflow The section has the following subsections: Web Service Example - Defining the Web Service Profile Web Service Example - Creating a Web Service Provider Workflow Web Service Example - Creating a Web Service Request Workflow Web Service Example - Running the Workflows
title: Web Service Example - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
